messages.content: What is the command to extract frames from a video file using ffmpeg in comfyui-ricklove?
The command to extract frames from a video file using ffmpeg in comfyui-ricklove is: ffmpeg -i input.mp4 out%05d.png
How can you convert HEIC files to PNG format in comfyui-ricklove?
In comfyui-ricklove, you can convert HEIC files to PNG format using the following command: find . -iname "*.heic" -exec heif-convert -q 100 {} {}.png \;
What is the command to convert a HEIC image to JPG format using ImageMagick in comfyui-ricklove?
The command to convert a HEIC image to JPG format using ImageMagick in comfyui-ricklove is: magick convert image.heic image.jpg
How can you batch convert HEIF images to JPG format using ImageMagick in comfyui-ricklove?
To batch convert HEIF images to JPG format using ImageMagick in comfyui-ricklove, you can use the following command: convert *.heif -set filename:base "%[basename]" "%[filename:base].jpg"
What is the command to convert HEIF images to PNG format using mogrify in comfyui-ricklove?
The command to convert HEIF images to PNG format using mogrify in comfyui-ricklove is: mogrify -format png *.heif
Who created the misc ComfyUI nodes?
The misc ComfyUI nodes were created by Rick Love.
What is the purpose of misc ComfyUI nodes?
The misc ComfyUI nodes are custom nodes that extend the functionality of ComfyUI.
